Input:
[0, 1, 0, 3, 12]
Steps:
Copy 1 → [1, _, _, _, _]

Copy 3 → [1, 3, _, _, _]

Copy 12 → [1, 3, 12, _, _]

Fill zeros → [1, 3, 12, 0, 0]
